1 pound of ground beef
1 half bunch of cilantro
1 thumb of ginger -- minced
3 cloves of garlic -- minced
1 nose of shallot -- minced
2 ripe plum tomatos -- diced

roasted cumin seeds -- mortered
roasted coriander seeds -- mortered

pita bread, halved and slighly tosted

2 ripe mangos -- in half-moons

Reduce cooked beef/pork/n mixture with vegitables and spices -- until it look s sloppy. Assemble fresh sprigs of cilantro, mango tranches, and mixture in a toasted pita pocket and serve.
